Kunci is a Rust implementation of Clevis and Tang for network-bound disk
encryption workflows.

This port packages the client and server binaries together with the FreeBSD
boot-time ZFS unlock helper script.

Installed components:
- kunci: client command-line interface
- kunci-server: Tang server daemon
- kunci_zfs: rc.d helper for boot-time ZFS unlock

WWW: https://github.com/hazayan/kunci
